Well, you must, sometimes.

524
00:27:00,650 --> 00:27:03,320
我有段时间很在乎他
He meant a lot to me for a while.

525
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:05,960
但都是过去了
But that's done now.

526
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,200
那你呢
What about you?

527
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,610
我什么
What about me?

528
00:27:14,050 --> 00:27:15,860
你觉得不满足吗
Are you unsatisfied?

529
00:27:18,860 --> 00:27:20,920
我们现在要时时处处小心
There's just too much at stake now.

530
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,970
没法信任任何人
No one we can trust.

531
00:27:23,820 --> 00:27:25,970
