Maybe it's better this way.

533
00:27:34,470 --> 00:27:36,410
不会分心
No room for distractions.

534
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:39,890
我不介意牺牲
I don't mind the sacrifice.

535
00:27:40,650 --> 00:27:42,330
我们选择了这个
