Took 85 years to complete it.

546
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,380
这座桥建了多久
How long did it take to complete the bridge.

547
00:28:18,380 --> 00:28:20,090
大概四年
Uh, about four years.

548
00:28:20,090 --> 00:28:23,320
罗斯福第二次就职演说后不久通行
It opened a few months after FDR's second inaugural.

549
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,920
